- Flux/Helm
- Palo Alto Firewalls
- Azure Firewall
- Hub and Spoke Network Architecture
- Panorama Management
- GitHub and source control
- Azure DevOps Pipeline
- Azure FrontDoor
- Application Gateway
- DNS Zones

You will have a feel of the HMCTS landscape to help you navigate your way through your epics and tasks.

